{"quote": "Lawyer Father Legend", "page_title": "Hook", "page_bio": "Hook (film) is a 1991 in film that tells the story of Peter Banning, a middle-aged business man who returns with his family to London, and the orphanage where he was raised. While there, his children are kidnapped and a note is left signed by \"J. Hook, Captain\". Wendy, the woman who raised Peter, tells him that the Peter Pan stories are true, and that he, Peter Banning is actually the boy who said he would never grow up. Peter must return to Neverland and find his forgotten childhood in order to save his family.", "page_url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hook (film)"}